&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Veronica Greenwood - Head of Orthoptic Services: veronica.greenwood@mft.nhs.uk or Lis Parry - Deputy Head Orthoptist: elisabeth.parry@mft.nhs.uk&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel 0161 276 5539&lt;/p&gt;
